1
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,799
Don't just stand there.

2
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:41,560
Say hi to him.

3
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,519
Hi.

4
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:00,280
I'm leaving.

5
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,280
Come back.

6
00:02:08,159 --> 00:02:09,199
So rude.

7
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,000
Sit down.

8
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:23,879
Why does it look like

9
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,560
you two know each other?

10
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,840
Were you classmates?

11
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:32,439
We were…

12
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,080
not close.

13
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:36,919
You skipped school.

14
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:37,960
So you knew no one.

15
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:38,800
You know,

16
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,000
her grades.

17
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:41,919
Too bad.

18
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:44,599
Why didn't she take the gaokao?

19
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:46,439
Well,

20
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:48,159
She was frail growing up.

21
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:50,199
She had a fever on gaokao day.

22
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,560
So it affected

23
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,759
her gaokao score.

24
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,639
And after that—

25
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:56,639
I'll retake it.

26
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,319
Ms. Guo promised

27
00:03:00,319 --> 00:03:01,759
to support me

28
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,599
through college.

29
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:06,199
Right.

30
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,439
She found one up north,

31
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:09,520
a prep school.

32
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,479
She'll be leaving soon.

33
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:14,919
You're so kind.

34
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,439
Never saw that side of you.

35
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,439
If that's the case,

36
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,879
Wan needs a prep year,

37
00:03:19,919 --> 00:03:22,120
Xixiao has art school applications.

38
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,000
Why don't you stay with us?

39
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,919
Xixiao doesn't study much.

40
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,360
Stay by his side,

41
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:30,759
set him an example.

42
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,439
No need.

43
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:37,199
I… I'm usually

44
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:39,120
used to being alone.

45
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:40,520
Exactly.

46
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:42,240
Don't pressure her.

47
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,879
She hates being a bother.

48
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:45,240
Too much pressure.

49
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:48,840
Fine by me.

50
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:52,759
I can learn a lot

51
00:03:52,759 --> 00:03:53,680
from you.

52
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:54,479
Really?

53
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,599
See? Xixiao agreed.

54
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,120
Why be

55
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,000
shy?

56
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,400
Ms. Chen.

57
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,639
Set up Xixiao's old room

58
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,560
from childhood.

59
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:08,639
That room.

60
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,879
He drew a lot there.

61
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:10,879
The walls are messy.

62
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:11,800
Please don't mind.

63
00:04:13,759 --> 00:04:15,960
I'll give you one year.

64
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:17,399
But…

65
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,279
Your mom's school

66
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:20,279
is hard to get into.

67
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,519
Are you confident?

68
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:22,759
Yes.

69
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,199
Listen, Lu Xixiao.

70
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,240
If during this year,

71
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,240
you stir up trouble

72
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,759
at home,

73
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:32,240
any trouble at all,

74
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,160
then don't you dare

75
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:34,800
pretend

76
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,199
you're working hard.

77
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:36,879
Are we clear?

78
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,240
Go abroad properly

79
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,360
and study finance.

80
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,000
Promise?

81
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,839
Fine.

82
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,160
Fine then.

83
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,319
It's settled.

84
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,199
Let's eat. Come on.

85
00:05:08,199 --> 00:05:09,199
Waiting on who?

86
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:10,120
Go play.

87
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:19,000
You'll live

88
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,360
together every day.

89
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,279
Must you be

90
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:21,920
Awkward?

91
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,040
What?

92
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,600
I said,

93
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,199
you'll live

94
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:25,240
every day anyway.

95
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,879
Why make it awkward?

96
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:33,759
I'm asking.

97
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,680
If one day,

98
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,439
Gu Meng became family,

99
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:41,560
what then?

100
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,399
What else?

101
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:43,360
Get along with her.

102
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,120
Gu Meng and I

103
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,360
aren't like you two.

104
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,399
We're special.

105
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:49,439
We have a deep bond.

106
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,000
What's with you two?

107
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,839
Tell me.

108
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,959
Do you know how many times

109
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:56,639
my name was in her notebook?

110
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,319
Fifty-seven times.

111
00:05:58,319 --> 00:06:00,160
Fifty-seven times, man.

112
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,040
Know what that means?

113
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,160
Unforgettable.

114
00:06:05,439 --> 00:06:06,439
Sometimes I admire

115
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:07,560
how your mind works.

116
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,240
I mean it.

117
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,480
You can fool yourself that hard.

118
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,959
I could never be that blind.

119
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:15,160
You call yourself not blind?

120
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,160
Deep down,

121
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,079
you'd be happy.

122
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,879
What? Say that again.

123
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:23,759
Drop it.

124
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,720
Forget it, okay?

125
00:06:29,879 --> 00:06:31,240
Finish the story, Wan.

126
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:32,480
What's up

127
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,560
with you two?

128
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,319
She's in hospital.

129
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:36,560
She's worried about me.

130
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:37,680
That place

131
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,800
is near the hospital.

132
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:40,600
Who asked you that?

133
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,959
I mean you and him.

134
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,600
And you two

135
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,519
added WeChat back.

136
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,319
They let you visit too.

137
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,360
Then why

138
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,079
fight again?

139
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,360
It's messy.

140
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,399
Tell me more.

141
00:06:59,839 --> 00:07:01,319
The woman who

142
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:02,920
helped me

143
00:07:04,079 --> 00:07:05,240
is sort of his stepmom.

144
00:07:06,399 --> 00:07:07,360
He dislikes her.

145
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:08,439
Our bond

146
00:07:08,439 --> 00:07:09,639
was never pure.

147
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,439
Then what

148
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:13,399
are you two now?

149
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,959
Live-in roommates,

150
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:15,800
god-siblings.

151
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,199
You two beat

152
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,360
Mom's soaps

153
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,120
hands down.

154
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,959
All right.

155
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:21,439
We should get going.

156
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,800
He likely doesn't

157
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,639
want to see me.

158
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,360
Then why let you go?

159
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:30,000
If it's a mix-up,

160
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,360
then clear it up.

161
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,759
If you messed up,

162
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:33,800
then apologize.

163
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,040
It's simple.

164
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:35,920
You must…

165
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,759
You scared me! Are you crazy?

166
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:39,759
Movie, remember?

167
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,439
Come on.

168
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:42,920
I told you to wait there.

169
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,439
I'll go from Wan's.

170
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,759
Why bother?

171
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,959
Look, what's this?

172
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,600
Look, what's that?

173
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,360
I came to pick you up.

174
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,600
So cool.

175
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,759
No cab needed.

176
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:53,959
Cool or not?

177
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,759
It's okay.

178
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,600
Go watch it.

179
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,519
I'm leaving.

180
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,040
Bye.

181
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,319
Bye.

182
00:07:58,319 --> 00:07:58,800
Fine.

183
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,160
Remember my words, Wan.

184
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:09,600
I'll get it.

185
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:10,560
No.

186
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,199
This way.

187
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:11,759
Thank you.

188
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:46,960
Here.

189
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:50,480
I've packed your

190
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,559
luggage.

191
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:56,360
What I said at dinner

192
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:58,720
wasn't just for him.

193
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,840
Right?

194
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:01,720
I know.

195
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:02,879
Go on.

196
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,600
About the wedding,

197
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:07,559
we may need to push it back.

198
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:08,320
Dad says wait

199
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:10,120
until Xixiao leaves next year.

200
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,799
Also,

201
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:13,759
You…

202
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,799
know your place

203
00:09:16,799 --> 00:09:18,279
in this family.

204
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,120
In this family,

205
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,840
I have enough

206
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:21,879
trouble already.

207
00:09:25,039 --> 00:09:25,799
Got it.

208
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:31,600
Miss me.

209
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,279
And that…

210
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,360
so-called little girl of yours.

211
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,000
Watch her.

212
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,080
Careful.

213
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,399
This room

214
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:08,879
has no private bathroom.

215
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,879
The bathroom is outside.

216
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,879
This is it.

217
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,360
Thank you.

218
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,159
Come in.

219
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:25,600
Tell me

220
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,720
if anything's missing.

221
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:28,440
Thank you.

222
00:10:29,799 --> 00:10:30,879
Get some rest early.

223
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:32,240
Need anything,

224
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,000
tell me.

225
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,200
Thank you.

226
00:10:34,399 --> 00:10:34,879
Okay.

227
00:10:34,879 --> 00:10:35,919
Not at all.

228
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,440
Lu Xixiao.

229
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,600
I never thought

230
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,480
I'd get this close

231
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,519
to your childhood.

232
00:11:58,799 --> 00:11:59,559
I… didn't know

233
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:00,360
it was occupied.

234
00:12:06,919 --> 00:12:08,000
Don't you have

235
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,120
your own bathroom?

236
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:12,039
Bossing me now?

237
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,679
Done?

238
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,840
Now that you've moved in,

239
00:12:18,559 --> 00:12:19,840
should've come say hi?

240
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,639
I thought you hated me.

241
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:26,559
And you?

242
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,759
Want to see me?

243
00:13:04,399 --> 00:13:05,000
I…

244
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:07,000
didn't know it'd go this way.

245
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:12,559
I didn't mean to upset you.

246
00:13:15,559 --> 00:13:16,320
And the result?

247
00:13:17,879 --> 00:13:18,960
Still the same?

248
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:24,759
Do you have time?

249
00:13:28,639 --> 00:13:29,360
Wan.

250
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:31,360
Bathroom's occupied.

251
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,600
Use mine in my room.

252
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:39,679
Come on.

253
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,679
Your godmother's calling.

254
00:13:43,759 --> 00:13:44,399
Little one.

255
00:13:55,559 --> 00:13:57,279
Is moving in fun for you?

256
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,120
Did you think

257
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,679
this would scare me?

258
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,240
Of course not.

259
00:14:04,279 --> 00:14:05,720
I didn't choose this.

260
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,600
It's for Grandma, that's all.

261
00:14:09,639 --> 00:14:11,279
It's been a while.

262
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:13,960
Still not used to

263
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,840
me as your daughter?

264
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,639
Dinner's ready.

265
00:14:40,279 --> 00:14:40,879
Mom.

266
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,759
I washed some fruit for you.

267
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:44,559
Here.

268
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:45,960
Have some fruit.

269
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:48,720
Well…

270
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:50,399
Wan.

271
00:14:51,039 --> 00:14:52,080
Guo Yan and I

272
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,799
haven't been in touch for years.

273
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:56,039
Sending so much at once…

274
00:14:56,799 --> 00:14:57,799
That feels off.

275
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,440
What's wrong with it?

276
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:02,200
Aren't we family, Mom?

277
00:15:04,360 --> 00:15:05,519
If she wants to,

278
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,120
just accept them.

279
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,320
These years,

280
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,840
Wan has really grown up.

281
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:14,000
Your love wasn't wasted.

282
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,600
I brought dinner.

283
00:15:20,279 --> 00:15:21,000
I'll do it.

284
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:21,559
No need.

285
00:15:21,559 --> 00:15:22,519
Leave it. Leave it.

286
00:15:22,519 --> 00:15:23,080
I'll do it.

287
00:15:23,639 --> 00:15:25,159
You're making it worse.

288
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:26,879
Get the dishes.

289
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,919
Mom, I'll get going then.

290
00:15:43,759 --> 00:15:44,519
150,000 yuan.

291
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,279
It's for Grandma's treatment.

292
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,480
A transplant costs 300,000 yuan.

293
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,120
This is only half.

294
00:15:57,000 --> 00:16:00,039
The rest has a condition.

295
00:16:06,679 --> 00:16:07,399
What terms?

296
00:16:09,679 --> 00:16:11,320
Don't you think

297
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,480
one year is too long?

298
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:15,200
If he studies finance,

299
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,799
after this summer

300
00:16:17,639 --> 00:16:18,799
would be perfect.

301
00:16:22,559 --> 00:16:23,879
You want him gone

302
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,000
to join the Lus.

303
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:28,360
Zhou Wan, I have ways

304
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:29,200
to make him go.

305
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:30,240
It's just that

306
00:16:30,519 --> 00:16:31,919
you need to do your part.

307
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:38,960
You want me to

308
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:39,960
make him leave.

309
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:41,279
Yes.

310
00:16:41,559 --> 00:16:42,279
Great.

311
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:44,039
If you manage it,

312
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:46,120
all the Lus will thank you.

313
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,000
After all, no one

314
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:49,120
wants him to do art.

315
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,279
I won't agree.

316
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:52,159
This money

317
00:16:52,159 --> 00:16:53,200
was owed to me.

318
00:16:58,279 --> 00:16:59,639
Grandma needs treatment.

319
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:02,799
Are you going to choose

320
00:17:03,159 --> 00:17:04,319
between Grandma

321
00:17:04,319 --> 00:17:05,480
and Lu Xixiao?

322
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,559
Grandma's illness is serious.

323
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:12,000
She can't wait long.

324
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:13,559
What if I

325
00:17:13,559 --> 00:17:14,359
expose you?

326
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,440
Crazy, Guo?

327
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,720
Expose me for what?

328
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,960
Go expose me.

329
00:17:18,279 --> 00:17:19,480
You'd have told him.

330
00:17:19,599 --> 00:17:21,039
Xixiao would know by now.

331
00:17:21,319 --> 00:17:22,279
But he doesn't.

332
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:24,920
Because you care.

333
00:17:25,480 --> 00:17:26,400
He'd get hurt.

334
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,279
so you hid everything.

335
00:17:29,359 --> 00:17:30,000
Besides,

336
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,519
What good would it do

337
00:17:31,519 --> 00:17:32,799
to kick me out?

338
00:17:33,079 --> 00:17:34,880
If I'm broke, how can I pay?

339
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,440
We're family.

340
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,160
We rise and fall together.

341
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:41,240
Don't you get it?

342
00:17:42,759 --> 00:17:43,799
What he studies

343
00:17:44,799 --> 00:17:45,640
or wants to do

344
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,480
isn't up to me.

345
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,839
And this is

346
00:17:48,839 --> 00:17:49,799
what he wants most.

347
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:53,640
That's none of my business.

348
00:17:55,119 --> 00:17:56,559
I need him abroad ASAP.

349
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,480
Then I can join the Lus.

350
00:17:59,079 --> 00:18:00,279
He has to leave.

351
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:05,599
This money isn't free.

352
00:18:19,079 --> 00:18:19,640
Xixiao.

353
00:18:23,599 --> 00:18:24,839
Let me see. I'll…

354
00:18:26,559 --> 00:18:27,799
He's sick. You knew?

355
00:18:30,039 --> 00:18:30,920
No way.

356
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,440
You two live together.

357
00:18:34,559 --> 00:18:35,440
I've been caring

358
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,240
for Grandma.

359
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,519
I didn't see him.

360
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:39,200
Thought he was out.

361
00:18:40,839 --> 00:18:41,720
Unbelievable.

362
00:18:42,279 --> 00:18:43,000
So close,

363
00:18:43,359 --> 00:18:44,599
acting like strangers?

364
00:19:01,799 --> 00:19:02,440
Ms. Chen.

365
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:03,400
Wan.

366
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,079
I bought some things.

367
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,680
He might like them.

368
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,559
Exactly.

369
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:10,319
He didn't touch his food

370
00:19:10,799 --> 00:19:11,839
or his meds.

371
00:19:12,559 --> 00:19:13,559
Take these to him.

372
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,839
He won't let me in.

373
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,359
How could that be?

374
00:19:19,079 --> 00:19:20,680
If he agreed to let you move in,

375
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,319
he must want to see you.

376
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:24,400
He doesn't want to see me.

377
00:19:25,519 --> 00:19:26,200
Go on.

378
00:19:26,599 --> 00:19:27,960
Take his medicine too.

379
00:19:28,599 --> 00:19:29,079
Go on.

380
00:19:31,039 --> 00:19:31,480
Go.

381
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,319
What now?

382
00:19:37,319 --> 00:19:38,240
You just left.

383
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,200
Why are you back?

384
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:40,799
It's me.

385
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:46,759
Come in.

386
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:56,759
I got you some Sanxian noodles.

387
00:19:58,119 --> 00:19:59,200
Eat a little.

388
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:04,720
So you came.

389
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,240
I thought you were mad.

390
00:20:16,119 --> 00:20:17,720
So you feared I was mad

391
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,759
and stayed away?

392
00:20:27,279 --> 00:20:27,839
Fine.

393
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:29,160
Good enough excuse.

394
00:20:30,599 --> 00:20:31,720
Then I was angry.

395
00:20:34,319 --> 00:20:35,640
You're… not mad?

396
00:21:17,759 --> 00:21:19,240
Take your medicine.

397
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,839
Turn the AC up.

398
00:21:28,559 --> 00:21:30,039
Bundle up

399
00:21:30,039 --> 00:21:30,799
sweat it out.

400
00:21:31,559 --> 00:21:32,640
Rest for two days.

401
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,039
I'll head back.

402
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,079
Wait.

403
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:48,920
Leaving?

404
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:53,480
So heartless.

405
00:21:54,319 --> 00:21:55,359
How'd I get sick?

406
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:58,240
That day,

407
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,400
I went back for you.

408
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:01,200
You were gone.

409
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:06,599
Then I'll stay longer.

410
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,279
Take your meds.

411
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:27,920
Are you okay?

412
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,319
He didn't bother you?

413
00:22:30,279 --> 00:22:30,920
No.

414
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:32,839
Don't worry.

415
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,319
Will you come back soon?

416
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:57,599
You said stay,

417
00:22:58,119 --> 00:22:58,839
Still busy.

418
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:06,880
I did nothing.

419
00:23:07,559 --> 00:23:08,680
This is my phone.

420
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:17,519
You what?

421
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:19,240
Got me sick.

422
00:23:21,559 --> 00:23:22,559
You said you'd stay,

423
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:23,839
bring me things.

424
00:23:25,319 --> 00:23:26,440
You call this company?

425
00:23:28,599 --> 00:23:29,880
What counts as sincere?

426
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:38,640
Share my misery.

427
00:23:42,359 --> 00:23:43,440
Catch my cold too.

428
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:08,880
So annoying.

429
00:24:11,319 --> 00:24:12,440
Eat the noodles.

430
00:24:13,039 --> 00:24:13,599
I'm off.

431
00:24:28,319 --> 00:24:28,880
Come in.

432
00:24:37,359 --> 00:24:38,599
I hope you like it.

433
00:24:44,279 --> 00:24:45,599
From Miss Zhou.

434
00:24:50,559 --> 00:24:51,079
Okay.

435
00:24:52,559 --> 00:24:53,319
Then I'll go.

436
00:25:22,039 --> 00:25:22,839
Morning.

437
00:25:23,759 --> 00:25:24,319
Morning.

438
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:26,240
Is your cold better?

439
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:27,400
Much better.

440
00:25:28,039 --> 00:25:28,759
Thanks to you.

441
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,319
That's good.

442
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:32,480
Come eat.

443
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:34,680
Feels like a family.

444
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,559
Xixiao, sit.

445
00:25:37,279 --> 00:25:38,319
I'm full. I'll go.

446
00:25:38,759 --> 00:25:40,240
So early? Where to?

447
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:41,200
Moon-gazing.

448
00:25:41,759 --> 00:25:42,319
Moon…

449
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:46,079
Ms. Chen.

450
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:48,720
Why the rush?

451
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:51,720
Xixiao's seeing Prof. Qin.

452
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,920
He has his portfolio.

453
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:56,359
This was on the table.

454
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,920
Maybe he forgot it.

455
00:25:58,599 --> 00:25:59,799
I'll take it to him.

456
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:01,200
Go slowly.

457
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:04,599
Prof. Qin.

458
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:06,640
I want the truth.

459
00:26:07,079 --> 00:26:07,799
What's wrong

460
00:26:07,799 --> 00:26:08,480
with it?

461
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:09,720
Are you sure?

462
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:12,039
It may sting.

463
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:13,799
Absolutely not.

464
00:26:14,359 --> 00:26:15,480
So confident.

465
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,480
If I feared the truth,

466
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:19,200
I'd still be on that road

467
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,359
racing for my life.

468
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:24,480
Are these

469
00:26:24,839 --> 00:26:26,079
all your works?

470
00:26:27,039 --> 00:26:27,599
Yes.

471
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:29,519
You're good.

472
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:30,680
Honestly,

473
00:26:30,759 --> 00:26:32,559
it should be fine.

474
00:26:33,359 --> 00:26:35,839
But I have little interest

475
00:26:35,960 --> 00:26:37,000
in tutoring you.

476
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:39,599
I can't help you.

477
00:26:40,039 --> 00:26:41,519
How could you not?

478
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:43,200
Prof. Qin, if you

479
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,400
were my tutor,

480
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:45,799
it would help a lot.

481
00:26:45,799 --> 00:26:46,079
Prof. Qin.

482
00:26:46,079 --> 00:26:46,880
I don't know

483
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,079
how to help you.

484
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:50,039
You keep drawing

485
00:26:50,039 --> 00:26:51,519
what your mother once drew,

486
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:52,319
don't you?

487
00:26:59,119 --> 00:27:00,079
You're very smart,

488
00:27:00,559 --> 00:27:01,640
like your mother.

489
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:04,240
But what I see is only imitation.

490
00:27:04,839 --> 00:27:06,920
I can't see where you are in it.

491
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:08,759
What you truly

492
00:27:08,759 --> 00:27:09,960
want to express.

493
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,559
Your inner emotions

494
00:27:12,079 --> 00:27:13,440
are completely absent

495
00:27:13,519 --> 00:27:14,480
from your work.

496
00:27:16,279 --> 00:27:16,799
Prof. Qin.

497
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:18,759
I can prepare again.

498
00:27:18,759 --> 00:27:19,279
Prof. Qin.

499
00:27:20,599 --> 00:27:21,119
Listen.

500
00:27:22,119 --> 00:27:23,720
Come back at month's end.

501
00:27:24,119 --> 00:27:25,000
I'll send it.

502
00:27:25,839 --> 00:27:28,319
But this will be your last chance.

503
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:29,839
Okay. I understand.

504
00:27:30,279 --> 00:27:30,880
Prof. Qin.

505
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:32,200
Well…

506
00:27:32,519 --> 00:27:35,079
what do you think

507
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,119
I should draw?

508
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:37,920
It's very simple.

509
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:41,160
Art is really about expression.

510
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:43,240
Expressing your own thoughts,

511
00:27:43,279 --> 00:27:44,680
your own feelings,

512
00:27:44,799 --> 00:27:46,000
your own heart,

513
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,480
your own emotions,

514
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:48,960
what you feel inside,

515
00:27:49,279 --> 00:27:50,680
what you want most,

516
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,440
what you fear losing most.

517
00:27:53,519 --> 00:27:55,400
The only difference is whether you

518
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:58,079
can face yourself.

519
00:27:59,839 --> 00:28:01,319
You're not foolish.

520
00:28:01,599 --> 00:28:03,160
I think you know.

521
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:04,680
I know.

522
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:07,319
But…

523
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:10,920
What I want

524
00:28:11,599 --> 00:28:12,680
is only in dreams.

525
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,440
Dreams are good material.

526
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:19,119
The real question is

527
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,680
what it means to you.

528
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:12,799
I can't see where you are in it.

529
00:29:14,119 --> 00:29:15,880
What you truly want to express.

530
00:29:16,720 --> 00:29:17,839
Your inner emotions

531
00:29:18,480 --> 00:29:19,640
are completely absent

532
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:20,559
from your work.

533
00:29:25,359 --> 00:29:27,160
What should I draw?

534
00:29:28,799 --> 00:29:29,960
Your own heart,

535
00:29:30,119 --> 00:29:31,359
your own emotions,

536
00:29:31,519 --> 00:29:32,839
what you feel inside,

537
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,519
what you want most.

538
00:29:35,160 --> 00:29:36,119
You know.

539
00:30:25,720 --> 00:30:26,279
What now?

540
00:30:26,279 --> 00:30:27,640
Are you fishing?

541
00:30:30,039 --> 00:30:30,559
Sweet?

542
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:33,359
Isn't this sweetener?

543
00:30:33,519 --> 00:30:34,640
Trying to fool me?

544
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:35,880
Sweetener's still sugar.

545
00:30:36,279 --> 00:30:37,000
Doctor said

546
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,440
your medicine's been bitter.

547
00:30:38,799 --> 00:30:39,480
After meds,

548
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:41,160
hold it, then spit it out.

549
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:42,799
It'll help the taste.

550
00:30:43,799 --> 00:30:45,440
Don't worry about me,

551
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:46,119
okay?

552
00:30:46,519 --> 00:30:47,880
Your prep year starts soon.

553
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:48,839
Focus on

554
00:30:48,839 --> 00:30:50,160
your prep year.

555
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,920
With my grades, why worry?

556
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,279
Forget paying tuition.

557
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:55,920
Even with scholarships,

558
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:56,920
they'd beg me

559
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,960
to enroll.

560
00:30:58,519 --> 00:31:00,319
I know you're smart.

561
00:31:00,519 --> 00:31:01,960
I know you're outstanding.

562
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:04,720
But it hurts me.

563
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,559
Look at other kids.

564
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,920
All they need to do

565
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:10,680
is study hard.

566
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:13,240
But besides school,

567
00:31:13,359 --> 00:31:14,799
you worry about me too.

568
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:19,880
Grandma only hopes

569
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:22,160
after your prep year,

570
00:31:23,039 --> 00:31:24,920
everything will go smoothly.

571
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:27,759
I don't expect

572
00:31:27,759 --> 00:31:28,680
your life

573
00:31:29,119 --> 00:31:30,160
to be successful

574
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,279
or dazzling.

575
00:31:33,119 --> 00:31:34,359
I only hope that

576
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:36,799
even if your life is ordinary,

577
00:31:36,799 --> 00:31:37,960
and plain,

578
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:42,000
you live kindly and happily.

579
00:31:45,759 --> 00:31:46,559
Grandma.

580
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:50,920
What makes someone kind?

581
00:31:52,240 --> 00:31:54,319
You are already very kind.

582
00:32:16,039 --> 00:32:17,000
Hello, Jiang Yan.

583
00:32:21,799 --> 00:32:23,519
I need your help with something.

584
00:32:25,119 --> 00:32:25,799
Can you?

585
00:32:57,160 --> 00:32:57,960
Mr. Lu.

586
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:58,960
Are you booked

587
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,319
to volunteer at ten?

588
00:33:04,599 --> 00:33:05,160
Yes.

589
00:33:11,079 --> 00:33:12,200
Please register here.

590
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:14,400
We've arranged

591
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,200
a volunteer

592
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:16,440
to guide you.

593
00:33:16,599 --> 00:33:17,440
Don't worry.

594
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:18,599
Wan?

595
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,359
With the kids

596
00:33:20,359 --> 00:33:21,480
for morning play.

597
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:24,119
I'll be your guide.

598
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:26,319
I often visit this home.

599
00:33:26,319 --> 00:33:27,279
I know it well.

600
00:33:27,759 --> 00:33:28,400
Questions?

601
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:29,000
Ask me.

602
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:30,079
Jiang Yan!

603
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:32,400
Back to class.

604
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,160
Play later,

605
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:33,720
okay?

606
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:34,359
Okay.

607
00:33:41,559 --> 00:33:42,240
Lu Xixiao.

608
00:33:48,279 --> 00:33:49,799
I was wrong last time.

609
00:33:51,559 --> 00:33:52,160
Wan chooses

610
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,200
who she sees.

611
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:54,359
Her choice.

612
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:55,720
I shouldn't meddle.

613
00:33:56,880 --> 00:33:57,480
I shouldn't

614
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,720
have dragged her

615
00:33:59,079 --> 00:34:00,319
into this.

616
00:34:01,920 --> 00:34:03,160
Don't waste her care.

617
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,839
Lead the way,

618
00:34:08,119 --> 00:34:08,920
Mr. Jiang.

619
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:14,760
Zhou Wan thought it

620
00:34:15,079 --> 00:34:16,599
might spark something.

621
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,400
Most kids here

622
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:21,960
keep to themselves.

623
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:24,480
But after a while,

624
00:34:24,679 --> 00:34:25,599
you'll see their

625
00:34:25,599 --> 00:34:26,320
innocence.

626
00:34:27,599 --> 00:34:28,840
If one gets tricky,

627
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:30,480
come to me or Zhou Wan.

628
00:34:32,199 --> 00:34:33,119
How hard is it?

629
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:36,519
The tiger is hunting.

630
00:34:36,679 --> 00:34:37,840
The deer and the piglet

631
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:39,519
