632
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:40,960
Oh no.

633
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,440
The old man fell down!

634
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:46,119
Which one is the old man?

635
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:49,920
Read on your own for a bit.

636
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,519
I'll join you later.

637
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:53,519
Sit here.

638
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,440
You really came.

639
00:35:01,559 --> 00:35:02,880
I was free anyway.

640
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,199
Why not

641
00:35:05,199 --> 00:35:06,039
