645
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,760
Introduce yourself.

646
00:35:34,800 --> 00:35:35,519
Start.

647
00:35:36,519 --> 00:35:37,800
Go, Shengsheng!

648
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:39,679
Go!

649
00:35:39,679 --> 00:35:40,519
Be careful.

650
00:35:40,519 --> 00:35:45,119
Go, go, go!

651
00:35:45,119 --> 00:35:46,320
You're really into this.

652
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,440
He's going to lose.

653
00:35:48,599 --> 00:35:49,039
No.

654
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,239
Against me?

655
00:35:56,519 --> 00:35:57,840
Wan!

656
00:35:59,400 --> 00:36:00,079
Go!

657
00:36:00,079 --> 00:36:00,480
Get up.

658
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:02,519
Wan, go!

659
00:36:02,519 --> 00:36:04,800
Wan, go!

660
00:36:05,679 --> 00:36:06,360
Okay, okay.

661
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,159
I won.

662
00:36:08,679 --> 00:36:09,840
Wan won!

663
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,679
Didn't you eat?

664
00:36:12,679 --> 00:36:13,239
No.

665
00:36:13,239 --> 00:36:14,159
Did you eat?

666
00:36:14,159 --> 00:36:14,719
No.

667
00:36:14,719 --> 00:36:15,360
Did you eat?

668
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:15,880
I didn't.

669
00:36:16,519 --> 00:36:17,679
Say, "I didn't eat."

670
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,719
Harder.

671
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,119
From then on,

672
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:25,199
they became best friends

673
00:36:25,639 --> 00:36:26,920
and lived

674
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,440
happily ever after.

675
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:31,920
Applause!

676
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:35,840
Did Jiang Yan do well?

677
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,920
Yes!

678
00:36:37,920 --> 00:36:39,719
Let's thank Jiang Yan.

679
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:43,840
Thank you, Jiang Yan!

680
00:36:43,840 --> 00:36:45,199
Next,

681
00:36:45,199 --> 00:36:46,320
Xixiao's turn.

682
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,000
Okay?

683
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,480
How does this work?

684
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:50,280
A little sheep.

685
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,400
Reach inside.

686
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,559
I want one too.

687
00:36:53,119 --> 00:36:54,000
Later.

688
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:56,119
I want a little lion.

689
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,159
Now we'll hear

690
00:36:57,159 --> 00:36:58,039
a new story.

691
00:36:58,039 --> 00:37:00,360
Quiet down, everyone.

692
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:04,199
Get ready.

693
00:37:06,199 --> 00:37:07,679
Long, long ago…

694
00:37:11,639 --> 00:37:13,639
Long, long ago…

695
00:37:16,679 --> 00:37:18,719
Same line again?

696
00:37:19,199 --> 00:37:20,760
So boring.

697
00:37:27,079 --> 00:37:28,679
This is no fun.

698
00:37:28,719 --> 00:37:30,280
Long, long ago…

699
00:37:31,679 --> 00:37:33,079
Long, long ago…

700
00:37:34,639 --> 00:37:36,599
there was

701
00:37:36,599 --> 00:37:39,760
a little black sheep.

702
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:47,360
She went to look for food

703
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:50,280
and met a big gray wolf.

704
00:37:58,639 --> 00:37:59,679
I'm scared.

705
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,360
She thought

706
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,239
the gray wolf

707
00:38:02,239 --> 00:38:03,599
was scary.

708
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:05,800
But then,

709
00:38:06,559 --> 00:38:07,360
the gray wolf

710
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:08,719
didn't want to hurt her.

711
00:38:14,920 --> 00:38:16,079
The gray wolf

712
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:18,199
lived alone in the forest.

713
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:20,159
He wanted no animals

714
00:38:20,159 --> 00:38:21,039
near him.

715
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:23,199
Because

716
00:38:24,239 --> 00:38:25,960
he looked so different,

717
00:38:27,119 --> 00:38:28,119
he hid away.

718
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:37,239
He thought she

719
00:38:37,239 --> 00:38:38,320
would fear him.

720
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,400
But to his surprise,

721
00:38:41,079 --> 00:38:42,519
she wasn't afraid at all.

722
00:38:44,199 --> 00:38:45,679
She wanted to play with him.

723
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:48,960
And the two of them

724
00:38:49,079 --> 00:38:50,360
had a great time.

725
00:38:52,199 --> 00:38:53,920
He invited her home.

726
00:38:54,599 --> 00:38:55,320
He thought

727
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,719
she wouldn't like it.

728
00:38:58,119 --> 00:38:59,199
But to his surprise,

729
00:39:01,199 --> 00:39:02,320
the little sheep said

730
00:39:03,719 --> 00:39:05,719
his home was

731
00:39:06,199 --> 00:39:08,599
the most beautiful,

732
00:39:08,599 --> 00:39:10,519
most beautiful place she'd seen.

733
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:14,119
They kept playing

734
00:39:14,119 --> 00:39:15,880
and playing together

735
00:39:17,480 --> 00:39:18,880
until it was getting dark,

736
00:39:19,199 --> 00:39:20,480
and she had to go home.

737
00:39:22,159 --> 00:39:23,039
Before she left,

738
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:25,760
the wolf stopped her.

739
00:39:29,079 --> 00:39:30,360
He gave her a flower.

740
00:39:32,119 --> 00:39:33,079
From his garden,

741
00:39:33,079 --> 00:39:34,239
