743
00:39:39,239 --> 00:39:40,639
The little sheep asked why.

744
00:39:43,119 --> 00:39:43,920
Why?

745
00:39:45,679 --> 00:39:47,159
Deep in the forest,

746
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,199
I built a garden.

747
00:39:51,360 --> 00:39:52,679
Everyone who came

748
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:56,280
saw only the gloomy path.

749
00:40:00,679 --> 00:40:01,440
Only you

750
00:40:02,639 --> 00:40:03,679
saw the roses.

751
00:40:06,639 --> 00:40:07,280
So…

752
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:12,519
