753
00:40:44,119 --> 00:40:45,880
Thank you, everyone.

754
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:47,039
Thank you, everyone.

755
00:40:51,079 --> 00:40:52,599
Let's thank Xixiao

756
00:40:52,599 --> 00:40:53,679
and Wan.

757
00:40:54,559 --> 00:40:56,440
Thank you, Xixiao.

758
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:58,199
Thank you, Wan.

759
00:40:58,199 --> 00:40:59,280
You're welcome.

760
00:41:35,639 --> 00:41:36,320
Xinyi.

761
00:41:36,679 --> 00:41:37,920
