762
00:41:38,679 --> 00:41:39,880
This is a Ferris wheel.

763
00:41:40,159 --> 00:41:41,559
This is a carousel.

764
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:43,719
What's this one?

765
00:41:44,559 --> 00:41:46,079
This is a bumper car.

766
00:41:46,920 --> 00:41:47,719
What's wrong?

767
00:41:47,920 --> 00:41:49,119
Does it not look right?

768
00:41:51,360 --> 00:41:52,320
Of course not.

769
00:41:52,679 --> 00:41:53,880
You drew it very well.

770
00:41:54,679 --> 00:41:55,719
When I was little,

771
00:41:55,719 --> 00:41:57,039
I rarely went there.

772
00:41:57,159 --> 00:41:58,880
so I didn't recognize it at first.

773
00:41:59,679 --> 00:42:00,519
It's okay.

774
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:02,519
On my next birthday,

775
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:04,280
come with me.

776
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:05,280
Okay?

777
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:07,079
Okay.

778
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,079
So?

779
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:33,159
Got inspired?

780
00:42:42,239 --> 00:42:43,239
What a day.

781
00:42:43,639 --> 00:42:44,519
I'm exhausted.

782
00:42:45,639 --> 00:42:46,480
I'm off.

783
00:42:48,239 --> 00:42:49,400
Want to try again?

784
00:42:53,480 --> 00:42:54,320
Next time.

785
00:43:31,159 --> 00:43:31,960
It didn't work?

786
00:43:37,920 --> 00:43:39,639
You did all this for him.

787
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:41,280
Why?

788
00:43:45,119 --> 00:43:46,280
I can't do much.

789
00:43:47,599 --> 00:43:48,519
Besides,

790
00:43:49,199 --> 00:43:50,320
I owe him this.

